Counting DP

State:
dp[state] = Number of ways to reach/build this state.

Transition:
dp[cur] += dp[prev]

Base Case:
Usually:
dp[start] = 1

Answer:
dp[target]

Common Transitions:
- Grid:
  dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j] + dp[i][j-1]

- DAG:
  dp[v] += dp[u]

- Stairs:
  dp[i] = dp[i-1] + dp[i-2]

Optimization:
max / min

Boolean:
OR

Counting:
SUM
